{"tid":2255045,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"左報偷拍鍾翰林 跟蹤判上判  台地檢轟偵探社為虎作倀","createTime":"2020-10-23T08:54:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T09:10:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6166e1c815d0c5d30e03611b7de31260139f3cfd","tid":2255045,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T08:54:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201023/7XHLPSO2LNGVTGDBGTPHZZK544/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201023%2F7XHLPSO2LNGVTGDBGTPHZZK544%2F&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vPolgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=d9151533\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201023%2F7XHLPSO2LNGVTGDBGTPHZZK544%2F&h=cc15395d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201023/7XHLPSO2LNGVTGDBGTPHZZK544/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n左報偷拍鍾翰林 跟蹤判上判 <br />\n台地檢轟偵探社為虎作倀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【多重黑手】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：被指涉煽動分裂 曾遭國安警拘捕<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】 前學生動源召集人鍾翰林去年在台灣與《自由時報》記者、台灣青年反共救國團理事長楊月清見面，全程遭跟蹤偷拍，事後《文匯報》及《大公報》頭版刊登總統蔡英文派出「密使」暗會港青。被屈成「密使」的記者及楊月清早前提控，台北地檢署調查後昨公佈內幕，偷拍者是台灣偵探社「一統徵信社」員工，收錢每日跟蹤鍾翰林，委託「一統」的是香港僑生李彬豪，他聲稱受香港私家偵探委託。地檢署認為證據不足以起訴涉案11人，但痛斥他們行為可鄙，李彬豪的留台許可或會廢止。<br />\n<br />\n兩份香港左報的跟蹤報道去年1月16日刊登，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OF4dgoULybvykDaG2ua2ECd2Ae0=/2658x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SFWF2QKU3VASJP2PWG6VOQBXSQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOF4dgoULybvykDaG2ua2ECd2Ae0%3D%2F2658x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSFWF2QKU3VASJP2PWG6VOQBXSQ.jpg&h=6fd45652&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■前學生動源召集人鍾翰林去年赴台灣全程被人跟蹤偷拍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eD18PDvcv7QFHcufN68GF9A5PYY=/1075x905/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2GUL4MV7IJFGNLOZFOUBYO6K4U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeD18PDvcv7QFHcufN68GF9A5PYY%3D%2F1075x905%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2GUL4MV7IJFGNLOZFOUBYO6K4U.jpg&h=fcf18fcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■《大公報》去年1月16日頭版刊登蔡英文派出「密使」暗會港青。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港僑生助找偵探社 稱無得益<br />\n<br />\n《自由時報》政治組副主任蘇永耀不滿私人行程曝光，提告「妨害秘密罪」，台北地檢署昨決定不起訴，但在不起訴書揭露更多內幕。原來鍾翰林一行三人從機場開始已被一統徵信社跟蹤，其後遊覽西門町、國史館，以及跟蘇永耀和楊月清見面全被偷拍。台警上門調查一統時，已找不到相關照片，總經理趙柏凱否認偷拍，只承認受託以每天兩萬元新台幣（約5,400港元）跟蹤鍾，共九名員工涉案，他表示一統受李彬豪委託。<br />\n<br />\n李彬豪受查時自稱香港人，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n本報追查發現，一名任職Pi、網名叫Pi Moriaty男子，跟李彬豪是fb朋友。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果》昨致電一統總經理趙柏凱，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n記者亦向香港偵探社Pi Investigation查問，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DhJSu34ILeKkcnR4LEENt1EN5mg=/2100x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5BQ5ZN2S4VCBVPX3HWRSLJCEXY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDhJSu34ILeKkcnR4LEENt1EN5mg%3D%2F2100x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5BQ5ZN2S4VCBVPX3HWRSLJCEXY.jpg&h=f1a0c06e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■偵探社Pi Investigation登記地址為長沙灣廣場一間商務中心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n證據不足 涉案11人未被起訴<br />\n<br />\n李彬豪昨未有接聽電話，翻查資料，李2015年就讀輔大心理系，台灣大學國際事務處網頁顯示，李彬豪今年是國際學生事務專員，負責「僑陸生申請入學」及「境外學生入學諮詢」。台警公佈涉案11人當中，除了九名一統人員和李彬豪，尚有一名是李的友人，未知是否跟三名退休港警接頭的「中國學生」。<br />\n<br />\n台灣檢方考慮被偷拍的地點是公眾場所，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n捲入事件的楊月清對未作檢控感失望，形容「放咗佢哋一馬」，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lgbkaiTzUdaKaV3qS73uYlpAoNI=/938x1173/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5WOCKRAIMFFGXBMD2KNR5DHBMM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlgbkaiTzUdaKaV3qS73uYlpAoNI%3D%2F938x1173%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5WOCKRAIMFFGXBMD2KNR5DHBMM.jpg&h=e1d972b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e06733bf2101b9ddc97c4bb6b7a93ada5122102","tid":2255045,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T09:07:22.000Z","msg":"條自稱香港人嘅共諜李彬州竟然係國際學生事務專員，負責「僑陸生申請入學」及「境外學生入學諮詢」。"},{"pid":"fa233ac800fc3a28c2256d7a0817c25888c0fbae","tid":2255045,"uid":40272,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T09:10:18.000Z","msg":"為虎作倀<br />\n記得係立法會講左好耐點讀 成個垃圾會得黃毓民識讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}